(198, 160, 4, 'Training for teachers and teaching classes for students in Lang Son, Quang Nam and Ben Tre.', 'training-for-teachers-and-teaching-classes-for-students-in-lang-son-quang-nam-and-ben-tre', 'news/2019/12/5e0acdc9346fe.jpg', 'The training for teachers and teaching classes for students are one of the series ofactivities under the framework of “Mizuiku – I love clean water” Program...', '<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img style=\"width: 550px; height: 306px;\" src=\"/pic/News/images/2019-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br /><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">In 2019, 17 schools in Lang Son, Ben Tre, Quang Nam and Dong Nai, are chosen to deploy &ldquo;Mizuiku &ndash; I love clean water&rdquo; Program including training for trainers,teaching classes for students, support teaching and learning materials, clean water filtration systems, schools&rsquo; walls painting and organizing recycle day.</span></span><br />&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img style=\"width: 550px; height: 413px;\" src=\"/pic/News/images/2019-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">The teachers participating in the training were the general teachers, teachers of grade 3,4 of 15 schools implementing the Mizuiku &ndash; I love clean water 2019 Program in Lang Son, Quang Nam and Ben Tre<br /><img style=\"width: 550px; height: 359px;\" src=\"/pic/News/images/2019-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span></span><br />&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><!-- [if gte mso 9]><xml>\r