(13, 9, NULL, 'course', 'General introduction about E-learning course', 'gioi-thieu-chung-ve-khoa-hoc-e-learning-2', 4, 'en', '<p>To further spread the message and meaning of \"Mizuiku - I love clean water\" program, E-learning online course for elementary teachers and anyone who is concerned about protecting their talents. water resources in particular and the environment in general are officially announced.<br />Objectives of the course:</p>\r\n<p>Help students understand the purpose and content, knowledge of water resources, learn the current situation, ways to save and protect water resources according to the lesson plan of the program \"Mizuiku - I love clean water\"<br />Contribute to improving capacity in teaching students about saving and protecting water resources by active educational methods.<br />Creating conditions for students to apply and deploy classroom models under the lesson plan of the \"Mizuiku - I love clean water\" program for children in schools and the community.</p>', 1, 442, '2018-09-19 11:43:00', '2019-12-30 09:51:17', NULL, 33, 33, NULL);
